title: Huge Third Person Kit v2.1
description: a new third person shooter online and offline modular kit
longDescription:
a new modular third-person shooter kit that includes inventory, guns, vehicles, character attachments, gun attachments,

ready to single and multiplayer, and much more stuff each third-person game needs.


Also, you can see all the project capabilities in the showcase


Notice: Before using the project Version 1 and 1.1, you have to enable the Chaos Vehicle plugin
